|---|---|---|
| **Security Headers** | None present | Added `helmet()` middleware |
| **DoS Protection** | No rate limiting | Added `express-rate-limit` |
| **Payload Safety** | No body parser / no size limit | Added `express.json()` with `10kb` limit |
| **Info Disclosure** | `x-powered-by` header exposes Express | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` |
| **Info Disclosure** | Stack traces leak on errors | Global error handler returns generic message |
| **Input Validation** | Query params not validated | Whitelist allowed params, validate types |
| **Error Handling** | No 404 handler | Explicit 404 JSON response |
| **Error Handling** | No global error handler | 4-param error middleware catches unhandled errors |
| **Configuration** | Hardcoded port | `process.env.PORT` fallback |

